    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行需要时间来权衡通胀不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德和她的首席经济学家表示，欧洲央行尚没有足够的证据表明通胀威胁已经过去——这加剧了人们对央行本月将暂停降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比亚迪销量因降价和技术升级创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/byd-sales-rise-to-a-record-on-price-cuts-tech-upgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻汇编的销售数据显示，由于降价和新技术激发了消费者的购买欲，比亚迪股份有限公司第二季度电动和混合动力汽车销量创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/byd-sales-rise-to-a-record-on-price-cuts-tech-upgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:01:59 GMT</pubDate>
